lead_paragraph: Australia have dropped out-of-form limited overs specialist Glenn Maxwell from the squad for the one-day international series in Sri Lanka next month, the country's cricket board announced on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Australia Axe Inconsistent Maxwell for Sri Lanka ODIs
headline.main: Australia Axe Inconsistent Maxwell for Sri Lanka ODIs
